            ("The Sprint Review is held:", "Sprint Review在以下時間舉行：", ["At the end of the Sprint to inspect the Increment and adapt the Product Backlog", "At the beginning of each Sprint", "Only when requested by stakeholders", "Every day during the Sprint"], ["在Sprint結束時檢查增量並調整產品待辦列表", "在每個Sprint開始時", "僅在利害關係人要求時", "Sprint期間每天"], 0, "Sprint Review is held at the end of the Sprint. Its purpose is to inspect the Increment and adapt the Product Backlog if needed. It's a working session, not a presentation.", "Sprint Review在Sprint結束時舉行。其目的是檢查增量並在需要時調整產品待辦列表。它是工作會議，而非演示。"),
